        "prompt": "=A 30 second cinematic ambient background score for a story about: {{ $json.story_text }}\nStyle: Melancholic lo-fi electronic, soft lonely piano, slow tempo, ethereal synth pads, glitchy mechanical textures, 65 BPM, somber atmosphere.",
